      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To direct the NIH to intensify and coordinate fundamental, translational, and clinical research with respect to the understanding of pain, the discovery and development of therapies for chronic pain, and the development of alternatives to opioids for effective pain treatments.</title>
